<p>&#272;&#7875; g&#7917;i th&#432;, h&atilde;y &#273;i&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave;o c&aacute;c h&#7897;p tho&#7841;i b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i. Y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u &#273;&#7875; g&#7917;i th&#432; l&agrave; th&ocirc;ng tin trong m&#7909;c &quot;N&#7897;i dung&quot;. B&#7841;n ph&#7843;i l&#432;u c&aacute;c thay &#273;&#7893;i tr&#432;&#7899;c khi chuy&#7875;n sang m&#7909;c (Tab) kh&aacute;c n&#7871;u kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7919;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i s&#7869; b&#7883; m&#7845;t. &#272;&#7875; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh th&#432; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&agrave; g&#7917;i ra ngo&agrave;i, h&atilde;y ch&#7885;n m&#7909;c &quot;Danh s&aacute;ch&quot;, ch&#7885;n danh s&aacute;ch mu&#7889;n g&#7917;i th&#432; v&agrave; b&#7845;m chu&#7897;t v&agrave;o n&uacute;t "G&#7917;i th&#432; t&#7899;i danh s&aacute;ch &#273;&atilde; ch&#7885;n".</p>
